=The Land of Warriors=

18
00:01:27,908 --> 00:01:29,980
(Adapted from Tangjia Sanshao's novel
"Soul Land")

19
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:34,340
=Episode 29=

20
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:36,029
It's vastly different.

21
00:01:36,030 --> 00:01:37,279
Our clan's top-notch secret weapon

22
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:39,660
can threaten the life
of a Grand Soul Master.

23
00:01:39,950 --> 00:01:41,469
Once you craft it,

24
00:01:41,470 --> 00:01:44,330
you'll be pioneering the forging world.

25
00:01:48,070 --> 00:01:49,149
Here's a part of the blueprint

26
00:01:49,150 --> 00:01:51,279
for the top-notch secret weapon,
the Storm Pear Blossom Needles.

27
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:52,980
Take your time to look at it thoroughly.

28
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:58,380
(Storm Pear Blossom Needles)

29
00:01:58,800 --> 00:01:59,629
Si Long,

30
00:01:59,630 --> 00:02:01,180
take them to rest.

31
00:02:01,550 --> 00:02:04,109
We still want to explore the auction.

32
00:02:04,110 --> 00:02:05,020
I wonder if you...

33
00:02:05,430 --> 00:02:06,589
It will be available tomorrow night.

34
00:02:06,590 --> 00:02:06,879
Titan,

35
00:02:06,880 --> 00:02:07,679
aren't you familiar with it?

36
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:09,290
You take them there tomorrow.

37
00:02:11,950 --> 00:02:12,679
Master.

38
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:13,890
Please don't bother me.

39
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:29,450
Young Master,

40
00:02:30,070 --> 00:02:31,199
This Lou Gao

41
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:32,879
has his own plans.

42
00:02:32,880 --> 00:02:33,989
Showing him a portion of the blueprint

43
00:02:33,990 --> 00:02:35,279
neither discourages his enthusiasm

44
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:36,679
nor risks leaking it.

45
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:39,149
It would only leave him wanting more.

46
00:02:39,150 --> 00:02:40,290
It's fine.

47
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:42,029
After he investigates the blueprint,

48
00:02:42,030 --> 00:02:44,060
he'll change his perceptions
towards the Tang Clan.

49
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:46,620
By then, I doubt he won't
think of running off.

50
00:02:46,630 --> 00:02:47,799
Moreover, I believe,

51
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,469
with his forging skills,

52
00:02:49,470 --> 00:02:52,660
he'll be a great asset
to the Tang Clan in the future.

53
00:03:02,630 --> 00:03:03,730
Mr. Si Long,

54
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:05,469
congratulations!

55
00:03:05,470 --> 00:03:07,180
Don't joke around with me.

56
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,399
Our president must've gone amiss.

57
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,879
I'll give him some advice tonight.

58
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:12,020
He won't.

59
00:03:12,070 --> 00:03:14,279
A blacksmith master
needs to possess skills,

60
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:16,620
and the most important thing
is his great insight.

61
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:19,149
Once Lou Gao investigated my blueprint,

62
00:03:19,150 --> 00:03:21,679
he'll discover the potential
of the Tang Clan.

63
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:24,580
Lou Gao has been focused
solely on forging, and nothing else.

64
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:25,679
For years,

65
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,839
the affairs in the Blacksmiths Guild
have been handled by you.

66
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:30,839
This time, it's perfect
for you to help out.

67
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:33,940
(Purchase List)

68
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,879
(50 jin of tungsten steel, 10 tons
of refined iron, 300 jin of pure silver)

69
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:37,149
Vice President Titan,

70
00:03:37,150 --> 00:03:38,330
is this real?

71
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:40,279
Ten tons of refined iron?

72
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:42,989
I've never seen anyone buy
that much refined iron at once.

73
00:03:42,990 --> 00:03:44,140
Alright,

74
00:03:44,470 --> 00:03:46,180
we'll purchase it at full price.

75
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:48,890
But we hope you can gather

76
00:03:48,950 --> 00:03:50,730
all the required metals for us quickly.

77
00:03:50,990 --> 00:03:51,770
No problem.

78
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,549
You traveled from afar,

79
00:03:54,550 --> 00:03:55,799
let me treat you to a meal.

80
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:56,679
I have a group of friend

81
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:58,629
who has just checked in
at the Tie's Inn.

82
00:03:58,630 --> 00:04:00,989
Why don't we go and meet them together?

83
00:04:00,990 --> 00:04:01,589
Sure.

84
00:04:01,590 --> 00:04:02,149
This way, please.

85
00:04:02,150 --> 00:04:02,589
Alright.

86
00:04:02,590 --> 00:04:03,220
Let's go.

87
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,180
Boss,

88
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:07,879
where can I find
those high-paying orders

89
00:04:07,880 --> 00:04:10,810
out of town that you just mentioned?

90
00:04:11,990 --> 00:04:13,450
My brother is also a blacksmith

91
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,980
and wants to earn some money.

92
00:04:17,550 --> 00:04:18,660
Fatty.

93
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:19,850
San.

94
00:04:21,400 --> 00:04:22,719
Grand Master Si Long,

95
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:23,770
please come in.

96
00:04:23,950 --> 00:04:25,069
Senior Si Long,

97
00:04:25,070 --> 00:04:26,239
this is Ma Hongjun,

98
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:27,450
one of my friends.

99
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:28,399
Fatty.

100
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:30,410
He's Senior Si Long.

101
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,879
Gather everyone downstairs.

102
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:34,239
We'll get a private room for dinner.

103
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,770
Senior Si Long is treating us.

104
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,620
Are we having the usual spot?

105
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:43,239
Um...

106
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:44,589
I'm sorry.

107
00:04:44,590 --> 00:04:45,949
Grand Master Si Long,

108
00:04:45,950 --> 00:04:48,239
that room has already
been occupied today.

109
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:50,980
But, the room is already reserved
long-term by the Blacksmiths Guild

110
00:04:51,840 --> 00:04:52,719
for hosting

111
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:54,140
important guests.

112
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:55,620
I know,

113
00:04:55,990 --> 00:04:57,290
but...

114
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:58,770
But what?

115
00:04:59,070 --> 00:05:02,330
It's all because the room

116
00:05:02,470 --> 00:05:05,500
has been reserved by me.

117
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:10,810
Myles,

118
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:12,220
what do you mean?

119
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:17,759
Grand Master Si Long

120
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:19,799
is a Grand Master Blacksmith.

121
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,509
Do you understand what being

122
00:05:21,510 --> 00:05:23,180
a Grand Master Blacksmith means?

123
00:05:23,630 --> 00:05:26,180
It's still just a blacksmith.

124
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:28,810
Don't grate on my ears!

125
00:05:28,990 --> 00:05:30,279
I'm famous

126
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:32,410
for being reasonable.

127
00:05:33,070 --> 00:05:36,069
As long as you convince Lou Gao

128
00:05:36,070 --> 00:05:38,069
to merge the Blacksmiths Guild

129
00:05:38,070 --> 00:05:39,359
into the Martial Soul Hall,

130
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,810
I'll make an exception

131
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:43,399
and allow you to use one of the rooms.

132
00:05:43,400 --> 00:05:44,500
Myles,

133
00:05:45,070 --> 00:05:46,180
don't forget.

134
00:05:46,470 --> 00:05:47,930
This is Gengxin City,

135
00:05:48,470 --> 00:05:49,770
the Capital of Metal.

136
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:53,100
Only blacksmiths are
the genuine masters here.

137
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:54,290
Yes.

138
00:05:54,950 --> 00:05:56,629
But, even the lord of Gengxin City

139
00:05:56,630 --> 00:05:59,810
has to bow to me.

140
00:06:00,280 --> 00:06:01,370
You...

141
00:06:01,510 --> 00:06:02,450
Get out of here!

142
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:13,330
(It seems that Myles
doesn't seem friendly.)

143
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:25,799
Sir,

144
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:26,839
that's them

145
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:29,290
who badmouthed the
Martial Soul Hall on the streets.

146
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:37,140
Senior Si Long,

147
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:40,799
are these ladies

148
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,700
coming along with you?

149
00:06:44,550 --> 00:06:46,220
What are they for?

150
00:06:46,550 --> 00:06:48,140
For you a blacksmith?

151
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:49,589
No way!

152
00:06:49,590 --> 00:06:50,700
I can't stand this anymore.

153
00:06:51,430 --> 00:06:52,319
Today,

154
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:54,239
you ladies come home with me.

155
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:56,580
Let me offer some advice for you.

156
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:10,069
I've tried so hard.

157
00:07:10,070 --> 00:07:11,980
How come I have no killing power at all?

158
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:14,250
I can't control my body anymore.

159
00:07:26,150 --> 00:07:27,890
Stop embarrassing yourself here!

160
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:32,540
It's you again.

161
00:07:32,760 --> 00:07:37,949
Aren't you the leader of the
Tribe of Strength, Titan?

162
00:07:37,950 --> 00:07:39,100
Yes, I am.

163
00:07:39,950 --> 00:07:42,199
If you want to oppose
against the Blacksmith Guild

164
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:43,799
and the Tribe of Strength,

165
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:45,770
I, Titan will accompany you for that.

166
00:07:48,630 --> 00:07:49,679
Yes, it's me again.

167
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,759
Any opinion?

168
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:52,509
You're not a blacksmith.

169
00:07:52,510 --> 00:07:54,429
Why are you so stubborn?

170
00:07:54,430 --> 00:07:55,429
Aren't you afraid

171
00:07:55,430 --> 00:07:57,799
that the Martial Soul Hall

172
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:59,580
will ruin the Tribe of Strength?

173
00:08:00,840 --> 00:08:03,069
(This Myles is far too arrogant.)

174
00:08:03,070 --> 00:08:05,250
(I wish I could throw him down
with the Eight Flinging.)

175
00:08:05,630 --> 00:08:06,730
(Don't rush!)

176
00:08:07,070 --> 00:08:09,980
(It's not time to deal with him yet.)

177
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:29,740
Elder Token!

178
00:08:38,800 --> 00:08:40,650
Greetings, Elder!

179
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,650
Greetings, Elder!

180
00:08:44,150 --> 00:08:48,180
We had no idea the Elder was here.

181
00:08:48,230 --> 00:08:49,410
Please forgive us.

182
00:08:50,310 --> 00:08:51,410
Please forgive us.

183
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:53,100
We'll discuss your punishment later.

184
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:57,189
Get out of here by rolling!

185
00:08:57,190 --> 00:08:58,100
Understood!

186
00:08:58,880 --> 00:09:00,060
Wait!

187
00:09:02,990 --> 00:09:04,330
Are you deaf?

188
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:07,690
The Elder said get
out of here by rolling!

189
00:09:13,560 --> 00:09:15,980
Understood.

190
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:19,530
What are you waiting for?

191
00:09:20,950 --> 00:09:22,610
Don't you know how to do it?

192
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:24,100
Shall I teach you?

193
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:26,879
Elder, they are newcomers.

194
00:09:26,880 --> 00:09:28,389
They're just too inexperienced.

195
00:09:28,390 --> 00:09:28,879
No worries.

196
00:09:28,880 --> 00:09:30,780
Let me be their example!

197
00:09:32,030 --> 00:09:33,140
Get down!

198
00:09:34,310 --> 00:09:35,900
Please guide us!

199
00:09:36,030 --> 00:09:37,180
Let's go.

200
00:09:38,110 --> 00:09:39,020
Let's go.

201
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,780
Carry on.

202
00:09:47,150 --> 00:09:49,250
(What a guy who changes
with the wind!)

203
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,530
(No worries.)

204
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:52,570
(I'll make them pay in the future.)

205
00:09:53,640 --> 00:09:55,029
Alright.

206
00:09:55,030 --> 00:09:56,940
It's just a farce!

207
00:09:57,230 --> 00:09:58,220
Si Long,

208
00:09:58,350 --> 00:09:59,439
hurry and take us to eat.

209
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:00,860
Everyone is hungry now.

210
00:10:01,030 --> 00:10:02,020
Wait a moment.

211
00:10:02,640 --> 00:10:03,690
You guys

212
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:06,820
are from the Martial Soul Hall?

213
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:12,780
Senior Si Long,

214
00:10:12,950 --> 00:10:14,330
let's eat first.

215
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:16,250
This,

216
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:18,020
I'll explain to you later.

217
00:10:29,230 --> 00:10:29,759
Sir,

218
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:30,980
do we still need to roll ourselves?

219
00:10:37,390 --> 00:10:38,639
Hold on, when did our Martial Soul Hall

220
00:10:38,640 --> 00:10:40,559
have such a young Elder?

221
00:10:40,560 --> 00:10:41,410
Is it possible?

222
00:10:41,640 --> 00:10:43,060
I really don't know.

223
00:10:43,110 --> 00:10:43,780
Sir,

224
00:10:44,030 --> 00:10:45,839
do you think that the guy
is messing with us?

225
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:47,650
Could that token be fake?

226
00:10:48,950 --> 00:10:49,149
Wait.

227
00:10:49,150 --> 00:10:50,820
Do you think I'm so dumb

228
00:10:51,640 --> 00:10:54,100
that I can't tell the difference
between a fake and a real token?

229
00:10:55,560 --> 00:10:57,180
I dare not.

230
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:59,229
But, if the token is real,

231
00:10:59,230 --> 00:11:00,989
and if Her Holiness did send
the Elder here to Gengxin City,

232
00:11:00,990 --> 00:11:03,020
why didn't she inform you in advance?

233
00:11:03,350 --> 00:11:04,919
Plus, he is mingling
with the Tribe of Strength

234
00:11:04,920 --> 00:11:06,919
and the Blacksmith Guild.

235
00:11:06,920 --> 00:11:08,490
It just doesn't make sense.

236
00:11:08,640 --> 00:11:10,450
The token may be real,

237
00:11:10,640 --> 00:11:12,370
but the person might not be.

238
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:14,349
Let's return

239
00:11:14,350 --> 00:11:16,389
and draft a letter to Her Holiness.

240
00:11:16,390 --> 00:11:17,599
We'll know whether he's real or fake

241
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:18,989
once we ask.

242
00:11:18,990 --> 00:11:23,380
(Tie's Inn)

243
00:11:26,350 --> 00:11:28,570
So, you're the son
of Grand Haotian Master.

244
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:29,799
I apologize for my disrespect earlier.

245
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:30,639
Senior Si Long,

246
00:11:30,640 --> 00:11:31,820
there's no need for such formalities.

247
00:11:32,030 --> 00:11:33,029
I only said that

248
00:11:33,030 --> 00:11:35,290
to avoid unnecessary misunderstandings.

249
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:37,900
Kid, don't worry.

250
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:41,060
We have no ties
to the Martial Soul Hall.

251
00:11:41,150 --> 00:11:43,250
If there's any connection to say,

252
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:44,980
it's only hostility.

253
00:11:45,270 --> 00:11:46,220
San,

254
00:11:46,230 --> 00:11:47,389
why didn't you

255
00:11:47,390 --> 00:11:48,980
teach those useless guys
a lesson just now?

256
00:11:49,950 --> 00:11:52,029
That Myles was so rampant!

257
00:11:52,030 --> 00:11:54,149
We should teach them
an unforgettable lesson.

258
00:11:54,150 --> 00:11:54,719
Fatty,

259
00:11:54,720 --> 00:11:56,060
your brain is not functioning again.

260
00:11:56,110 --> 00:11:56,879
We haven't even started
the initial plan yet,

261
00:11:56,880 --> 00:11:58,479
how could we go
against the locals openly?

262
00:11:58,480 --> 00:12:00,269
That Myles would probably
pinpoint the blame

263
00:12:00,270 --> 00:12:01,519
on the Blacksmith Guild.

264
00:12:01,520 --> 00:12:03,450
By then, Si Long and the others
would get into big trouble.

265
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:04,599
Ao,

266
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:06,940
what's there to fear
as San has the Elder Token?

267
00:12:07,030 --> 00:12:09,189
After all, I'm not the genuine
Elder of the Martial Soul Hall.

268
00:12:09,190 --> 00:12:10,389
That Myles will definitely try

269
00:12:10,390 --> 00:12:11,519
every way possible

270
00:12:11,520 --> 00:12:12,860
to figure out who I am.

271
00:12:12,990 --> 00:12:14,189
So, for now, what we need to do

272
00:12:14,190 --> 00:12:16,149
is to get our plan done here quickly

273
00:12:16,150 --> 00:12:17,389
and leave as soon as possible.

274
00:12:17,390 --> 00:12:19,530
So, we're just letting
Myles off like that?

275
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:20,989
How is that possible?

276
00:12:20,990 --> 00:12:22,820
Don't you know San yet?

277
00:12:24,030 --> 00:12:25,519
So, San,

278
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:26,519
do you

279
00:12:26,520 --> 00:12:27,719
already have a plan

280
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:29,180
to handle that Myles?

281
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:30,530
Don't act rashly.

282
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:32,450
Senior Si Long,

283
00:12:32,600 --> 00:12:33,559
can you

284
00:12:33,560 --> 00:12:35,109
tell us about the connection
between the Blacksmith Guild

285
00:12:35,110 --> 00:12:36,839
and the Martial Soul Hall?

286
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:38,180
They're incompatible
just like the water and fire.

287
00:12:39,390 --> 00:12:40,740
Uncle Titan knows this well.

288
00:12:40,880 --> 00:12:41,719
Back then,

289
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:43,639
Myles brought people
and created chaos for us.

290
00:12:43,640 --> 00:12:44,799
Although he didn't succeed,

291
00:12:44,800 --> 00:12:46,140
a grudge was formed.

292
00:12:46,350 --> 00:12:47,140
After that,

293
00:12:47,230 --> 00:12:48,919
he repeatedly brought
the Martial Soul Hall people

294
00:12:48,920 --> 00:12:50,349
to oppress the Blacksmith Guild,

295
00:12:50,350 --> 00:12:51,980
making trouble for us everywhere.

296
00:12:52,030 --> 00:12:52,949
Soon after,

297
00:12:52,950 --> 00:12:54,940
blacksmiths in the city
began disappearing.

298
00:12:55,310 --> 00:12:56,940
Everyone was terrified,

299
00:12:57,030 --> 00:12:59,530
no one dared leave their homes.

300
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:02,029
So, you suspect

301
00:13:02,030 --> 00:13:04,919
that the Martial Soul Hall is behind
the disappearance of blacksmiths?

302
00:13:04,920 --> 00:13:06,490
I'm certain it's them.

303
00:13:07,030 --> 00:13:08,650
After many blacksmiths disappeared,

304
00:13:08,760 --> 00:13:10,149
someone spotted

305
00:13:10,150 --> 00:13:11,109
the people from the Martial Soul Hall

306
00:13:11,110 --> 00:13:12,980
sneakily transporting weapons
out of the city at night.

307
00:13:13,150 --> 00:13:14,980
Other than the missing blacksmiths,

308
00:13:14,990 --> 00:13:17,330
who else could be
forging weapons for them?

309
00:13:17,640 --> 00:13:19,029
Did Lou not take action?

310
00:13:19,030 --> 00:13:20,140
Of course, he did.

311
00:13:20,230 --> 00:13:21,759
Master led us from the Blacksmith Guild

312
00:13:21,760 --> 00:13:23,330
to confront the Martial Soul Hall
for the missing people.

313
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:25,029
But, the eyewitness

314
00:13:25,030 --> 00:13:26,719
was too scared to testify.

315
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:28,149
Without evidence,

316
00:13:28,150 --> 00:13:28,759
we could not...

317
00:13:28,760 --> 00:13:30,330
Why do you need evidence?

318
00:13:30,350 --> 00:13:32,229
Just break in and find the people!

319
00:13:32,230 --> 00:13:33,530
Uncle Titan,

320
00:13:33,920 --> 00:13:35,759
you should know our situation better.

321
00:13:35,760 --> 00:13:37,690
Although our master and the rest of us

322
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:39,349
are Great Soul Master and Soul Saint,

323
00:13:39,350 --> 00:13:40,439
we've always

324
00:13:40,440 --> 00:13:42,229
focused on forging.

325
00:13:42,230 --> 00:13:43,740
If it comes to fighting,

326
00:13:43,950 --> 00:13:45,740
we may not be their match.

327
00:13:45,920 --> 00:13:47,140
We also don't dare

328
00:13:47,640 --> 00:13:49,490
spread this news lightly.

329
00:13:49,760 --> 00:13:50,860
Otherwise,

330
00:13:50,990 --> 00:13:53,180
it would only make it harder to approach
Myles and his people in the future.

331
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:54,879
(No wonder we hardly see)

332
00:13:54,880 --> 00:13:57,250
(any strong local men
since entering the city.)

333
00:13:57,680 --> 00:13:59,370
(The Martial Soul Hall
is secretly producing weapons.)

334
00:13:59,560 --> 00:14:01,650
(Bi Bi Dong must be
plotting something else.)

335
00:14:05,030 --> 00:14:06,439
When I first arrived in Gengxin City,

336
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:08,029
I sensed something was amiss.

337
00:14:08,030 --> 00:14:09,980
That's why I wanted
to learn more about the situation.

338
00:14:10,350 --> 00:14:11,799
The disappearance of blacksmiths

339
00:14:11,800 --> 00:14:13,180
is something we can't ignore.

340
00:14:13,310 --> 00:14:15,370
But, we can't alert the enemy either.

341
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:16,900
So, you're saying

342
00:14:16,950 --> 00:14:19,020
you want to help us find
the missing blacksmiths?

343
00:14:19,030 --> 00:14:20,100
We need

344
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:22,220
to investigate further first.

345
00:14:22,680 --> 00:14:24,349
For now, you just focus
on helping us to locate

346
00:14:24,350 --> 00:14:26,109
the ores and metals we need.

347
00:14:26,110 --> 00:14:27,229
Also, please arrange for us

348
00:14:27,230 --> 00:14:28,940
to attend tomorrow's auction.

349
00:14:29,030 --> 00:14:31,450
Got it. Leave it to me.

350
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:37,439
(Tie's Inn)

351
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:39,949
Ao and Si Long are busy
checking the purchase list.

352
00:14:39,950 --> 00:14:42,389
I believe that the Blacksmith Guild

353
00:14:42,390 --> 00:14:44,109
can quickly gather everything we need.

354
00:14:44,110 --> 00:14:45,220
Indeed.

355
00:14:45,920 --> 00:14:46,989
San,

356
00:14:46,990 --> 00:14:48,639
when do you plan to take action

357
00:14:48,640 --> 00:14:50,100
against the Martial Soul Hall?

358
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:53,940
A dark and stormy night

359
00:14:54,840 --> 00:14:56,220
is just perfect for action.

360
00:14:58,390 --> 00:15:00,439
I love taking action at night.

361
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:02,559
We'll take action
after tomorrow night's auction.

362
00:15:02,560 --> 00:15:03,530
Great!

363
00:15:03,600 --> 00:15:06,519
It's been a while
since I've performed myself.

364
00:15:06,520 --> 00:15:07,599
Elder Titan,

365
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:09,599
you're the vice president
of the Blacksmith Guild.

366
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:11,519
If you fight against
the Martial Soul Hall,

367
00:15:11,520 --> 00:15:13,599
it might cause trouble
to the Blacksmith Guild.

368
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:16,140
We need to take action discreetly.

369
00:15:16,350 --> 00:15:17,690
Just me,

370
00:15:17,720 --> 00:15:18,599
Fatty,

371
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:19,439
and Ao

372
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:20,799
will be enough.

373
00:15:20,800 --> 00:15:21,109
That's right.

374
00:15:21,110 --> 00:15:22,690
I'll stay back to take care of Wu.

375
00:15:22,990 --> 00:15:23,740
Good.

376
00:15:25,230 --> 00:15:26,450
Cousin San, what about me?

377
00:15:26,600 --> 00:15:28,149
Do you assign a task for me?

378
00:15:28,150 --> 00:15:29,220
Of course.

379
00:15:29,520 --> 00:15:31,650
It's something only you can do.

380
00:15:32,350 --> 00:15:35,439
You will go investigate the
Martial Soul Hall with Fatty tomorrow,

381
00:15:35,440 --> 00:15:36,599
and figure out

382
00:15:36,600 --> 00:15:37,949
what their current situation is,

383
00:15:37,950 --> 00:15:39,519
ensuring that our plan

384
00:15:39,520 --> 00:15:40,940
goes smoothly.

385
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:43,570
Master,

386
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:44,919
as per your instructions,

387
00:15:44,920 --> 00:15:46,639
I've gathered part of the
Martial Soul Hall's forces

388
00:15:46,640 --> 00:15:47,639
into a troop

389
00:15:47,640 --> 00:15:49,180
and awaited your next orders.

390
00:15:49,520 --> 00:15:50,610
Great!

391
00:15:50,720 --> 00:15:53,140
You're fully in charge
of this operation.

392
00:15:53,350 --> 00:15:55,330
Please work carefully with her.

393
00:15:55,920 --> 00:15:57,109
I trust

394
00:15:57,110 --> 00:15:58,980
that you won't disappoint me.

395
00:15:59,190 --> 00:16:01,020
I will do my utmost.

396
00:16:01,390 --> 00:16:02,490
In these few days,

397
00:16:02,640 --> 00:16:05,100
I'll go into a crucial
stage of my cultivation.

398
00:16:05,310 --> 00:16:06,599
Unless it's urgent,

399
00:16:06,600 --> 00:16:08,140
don't disturb me.

400
00:16:08,640 --> 00:16:09,490
Understood.

401
00:16:24,990 --> 00:16:26,599
The Holy Lady sent a message.

402
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:28,610
The soul masters have gathered.

403
00:16:28,920 --> 00:16:31,740
Your Highness, please get
ready for the next step.

404
00:16:33,560 --> 00:16:35,029
How much longer does he have?

405
00:16:35,030 --> 00:16:35,919
Your Highness,

406
00:16:35,920 --> 00:16:39,250
the poison has penetrated
into His Majesty's bone.

407
00:16:39,440 --> 00:16:41,940
He doesn't have long.

408
00:16:44,110 --> 00:16:46,530
I can't waste more time on Xue Beng.

409
00:16:47,230 --> 00:16:48,860
Has the news been released?

410
00:16:49,150 --> 00:16:49,980
Yes.

411
00:16:50,720 --> 00:16:51,820
Great!

412
00:16:54,990 --> 00:16:57,530
If you keep pushing yourself like this,

413
00:16:57,720 --> 00:17:00,940
your back injury won't heal.

414
00:17:04,270 --> 00:17:05,650
It's just a small injury.

415
00:17:06,920 --> 00:17:09,370
It's nothing compared to Father's life.

416
00:17:09,990 --> 00:17:12,530
Has Tang San finished
developing the antidote?

417
00:17:13,800 --> 00:17:14,799
I've checked the situation.

418
00:17:14,800 --> 00:17:16,349
The little devils have left the city.

419
00:17:16,350 --> 00:17:18,229
Before leaving, he made arrangements

420
00:17:18,230 --> 00:17:20,780
for reliable people to continue
developing the antidote.

421
00:17:21,030 --> 00:17:22,780
I'm just afraid Father
can't wait until it's ready.

422
00:17:22,800 --> 00:17:24,229
Send someone to the palace
to find more ways,

423
00:17:24,230 --> 00:17:26,060
and see if there's any other news.

424
00:17:31,840 --> 00:17:32,679
Here, take a look.

425
00:17:32,680 --> 00:17:33,919
High-quality ores!

426
00:17:33,920 --> 00:17:34,759
Abundant supply!

427
00:17:34,760 --> 00:17:36,029
Excellent quality at a fair price!

428
00:17:36,030 --> 00:17:37,570
No deceit, guaranteed for everyone!

429
00:17:37,950 --> 00:17:39,309
This is the largest ore trading market

430
00:17:39,310 --> 00:17:40,860
in Gengxin City.

431
00:17:41,110 --> 00:17:42,309
The ores here

432
00:17:42,310 --> 00:17:44,309
haven't been appraised
by the Blacksmith Guild,

433
00:17:44,310 --> 00:17:45,860
so the prices are cheaper,

434
00:17:46,600 --> 00:17:49,250
but it's also easier to get scammed.

435
00:17:49,560 --> 00:17:50,639
In my opinion,

436
00:17:50,640 --> 00:17:52,439
it's better to go to
the Blacksmith Guild's trading hall

437
00:17:52,440 --> 00:17:53,989
to buy ores that have
already been appraised.

438
00:17:53,990 --> 00:17:55,149
That's more reliable.

439
00:17:55,150 --> 00:17:57,519
Since Ao is there
sorting the ore purchases,

440
00:17:57,520 --> 00:17:58,839
both of you can pick it together.

441
00:17:58,840 --> 00:18:00,639
Thank you, Senior Si Long,
for considering this for us.

442
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:04,330
But, the appraised ores
are far too expensive.

443
00:18:04,520 --> 00:18:06,639
As the Tang Clan's treasurer,

444
00:18:06,640 --> 00:18:08,439
I must save wherever I can for San.

445
00:18:08,440 --> 00:18:09,450
But,

446
00:18:09,640 --> 00:18:10,949
please allow me to be frank,

447
00:18:10,950 --> 00:18:12,309
even experts can sometimes

448
00:18:12,310 --> 00:18:14,759
misjudge the ores here.

449
00:18:14,760 --> 00:18:16,439
Although I can help you inspect them,

450
00:18:16,440 --> 00:18:17,439
I can't guarantee

451
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:19,439
you'll be fully satisfied.

452
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:21,650
Take a look.

453
00:18:22,440 --> 00:18:23,690
Let's go over there and check it out.

454
00:18:32,800 --> 00:18:33,780
I want this one.

455
00:18:33,990 --> 00:18:34,820
Boss.

456
00:18:34,950 --> 00:18:36,180
1,000 gold soul coins.

457
00:18:36,230 --> 00:18:37,250
Cut it for me.

458
00:18:37,840 --> 00:18:38,490
Hold on.

459
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:42,220
You need to cut from this spot for me.

460
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:43,740
Sure.

461
00:18:45,150 --> 00:18:46,389
Slice the stone,

462
00:18:46,390 --> 00:18:47,389
and fortune rise.

463
00:18:47,390 --> 00:18:47,949
Good!

464
00:18:47,950 --> 00:18:49,180
Rise!

465
00:18:50,840 --> 00:18:51,559
Rise!

466
00:18:51,560 --> 00:18:52,879
Rise!

467
00:18:52,880 --> 00:18:53,269
Rise!

468
00:18:53,270 --> 00:18:53,839
Rise!

469
00:18:53,840 --> 00:18:55,410
Rise!

470
00:19:01,800 --> 00:19:03,149
One cut to heaven,

471
00:19:03,150 --> 00:19:04,530
one to hell!

472
00:19:04,560 --> 00:19:06,940
You will have it next time!

473
00:19:06,990 --> 00:19:07,740
Boss,

474
00:19:07,760 --> 00:19:08,309
your stone...

475
00:19:08,310 --> 00:19:09,250
Sigh.

476
00:19:09,310 --> 00:19:10,250
What a bad luck!

477
00:19:10,270 --> 00:19:11,330
It's a dud!

478
00:19:11,600 --> 00:19:12,309
That's

479
00:19:12,310 --> 00:19:13,309
how it is here.

480
00:19:13,310 --> 00:19:14,069
If it's a correct one,

481
00:19:14,070 --> 00:19:15,479
its value multiple dozen times.

482
00:19:15,480 --> 00:19:16,269
If it's a miss,

483
00:19:16,270 --> 00:19:17,860
it's not worth a single copper coin.

484
00:19:21,640 --> 00:19:22,559
Boss,

485
00:19:22,560 --> 00:19:23,799
this stone is useless now.

486
00:19:23,800 --> 00:19:24,599
Can I take it away?

487
00:19:24,600 --> 00:19:25,639
Who says it's useless?

488
00:19:25,640 --> 00:19:26,559
If the buyer doesn't want it,

489
00:19:26,560 --> 00:19:27,949
the stone reverts to me.

490
00:19:27,950 --> 00:19:28,719
If you want it,

491
00:19:28,720 --> 00:19:29,759
you've got to pay.

492
00:19:29,760 --> 00:19:30,690
Miss Ning,

493
00:19:30,920 --> 00:19:33,330
this stone is nothing but a dud.

494
00:19:34,110 --> 00:19:36,780
Oh, so this young lady
is a friend of Mr. Si Long.

495
00:19:37,110 --> 00:19:37,989
Mr. Si Long,

496
00:19:37,990 --> 00:19:39,439
I run a small business.

497
00:19:39,440 --> 00:19:42,250
If this young lady truly likes it,

498
00:19:42,440 --> 00:19:43,919
she can have it
with just one gold soul coin.

499
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:44,879
One gold soul coin?

500
00:19:44,880 --> 00:19:45,740
Deal!

501
00:19:49,070 --> 00:19:50,180
Thank you, young lady.

502
00:19:50,720 --> 00:19:51,799
Miss Ning,

503
00:19:51,800 --> 00:19:53,919
if you need this kind
of discarded raw stone,

504
00:19:53,920 --> 00:19:55,309
I can provide it to you for free.

505
00:19:55,310 --> 00:19:58,250
That vendor just wanted to rip you off.

506
00:19:58,350 --> 00:19:59,820
Senior Si Long, don't worry.

507
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:02,490
I might have just snagged a great deal.

508
00:20:09,190 --> 00:20:10,450
Why are you smiling?

509
00:20:10,720 --> 00:20:11,490
Look!

510
00:20:22,760 --> 00:20:24,309
It was just a discarded material.

511
00:20:24,310 --> 00:20:26,140
How could you possibly
see what's inside?

512
00:20:27,150 --> 00:20:29,900
A soul master with the
Qibao Amber Pagoda Martial Soul

513
00:20:30,150 --> 00:20:31,919
