strong appraisal ability.

514
00:20:31,920 --> 00:20:32,989
Oh, so you have such an ability?

515
00:20:32,990 --> 00:20:35,189
You're practically a born ore appraiser!

516
00:20:35,190 --> 00:20:36,940
No wonder Chief Tang

517
00:20:37,030 --> 00:20:39,020
sent you here to purchase ores.

518
00:20:39,110 --> 00:20:41,389
I should thank the previous buyer.

519
00:20:41,390 --> 00:20:41,949
Let's go.

520
00:20:41,950 --> 00:20:44,490
Today, I'm going to stock up
on the clan's treasury!

521
00:21:00,030 --> 00:21:02,900
These armors were shipped
out from Gengxin City.

522
00:21:03,270 --> 00:21:05,610
(They're heading toward the
direction of Tiandou City)

523
00:21:05,640 --> 00:21:08,020
It seems Bi Bi Dong is preparing
to take action against Tiandou.

524
00:21:08,190 --> 00:21:09,290
We need to go back instantly.

525
00:21:31,990 --> 00:21:32,940
Hurry up!

526
00:21:41,190 --> 00:21:42,060
Hurry up!

527
00:21:42,640 --> 00:21:43,570
Stay in line!

528
00:21:44,520 --> 00:21:45,220
Go!

529
00:21:47,440 --> 00:21:48,410
Go!

530
00:21:50,950 --> 00:21:52,060
Hurry up!

531
00:22:08,640 --> 00:22:09,389
The weapons and armor here

532
00:22:09,390 --> 00:22:11,330
are exactly the same as those in the
Martial Soul Hall of Xingluo City.

533
00:22:11,760 --> 00:22:14,799
It seems that Myles
has made a lot of money.

534
00:22:14,800 --> 00:22:15,389
Hurry up!

535
00:22:15,390 --> 00:22:16,450
Be quicker!

536
00:22:18,720 --> 00:22:19,650
Hurry up!

537
00:22:28,190 --> 00:22:29,220
Look!

538
00:22:45,560 --> 00:22:46,820
Help me!

539
00:22:46,880 --> 00:22:48,020
Uncle,

540
00:22:48,560 --> 00:22:49,900
