541
00:22:55,800 --> 00:22:56,490
Who's there?

542
00:22:57,310 --> 00:22:58,060
On alert!

543
00:23:01,030 --> 00:23:01,439
Something's wrong!

544
00:23:01,440 --> 00:23:02,389
Someone's in the back courtyard!

545
00:23:02,390 --> 00:23:03,330
Let's go!

546
00:23:04,680 --> 00:23:05,519
Take him away!

547
00:23:05,520 --> 00:23:06,639
I'll go distract them.

548
00:23:06,640 --> 00:23:07,229
Xiang.

549
00:23:07,230 --> 00:23:08,140
Trust me.

550
00:23:08,350 --> 00:23:09,290
Be careful.

551
00:23:14,880 --> 00:23:15,820
Delusion.

552
00:23:21,110 --> 00:23:22,650
Split up and chase them!

553
00:23:22,920 --> 00:23:23,980
Go!

554
00:23:38,270 --> 00:23:39,250
Sir!

555
00:23:39,640 --> 00:23:40,309
Sir!

556
00:23:40,310 --> 00:23:41,679
Those identical women

557
00:23:41,680 --> 00:23:43,370
suddenly disappeared
right before our eyes.

558
00:23:43,640 --> 00:23:44,189
Oh no!

559
00:23:44,190 --> 00:23:45,330
That's a soul skill!

560
00:23:45,480 --> 00:23:46,919
They discovered the bodies
in the back courtyard.

561
00:23:46,920 --> 00:23:48,100
Should we report to the lord?

562
00:23:48,190 --> 00:23:49,780
